{"tid":2328682,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"bidu 有人買百度嗎？","createTime":"2020-12-16T16:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T14:10:08.000Z","uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0816f659d30592dbc3bb6e4b7bf72d72e54893","tid":2328682,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"素有「女版巴菲特」之稱的 Cathie Wood 所操盤的 ARK 基金，連二日加碼買進中國科技股巨頭百度 (BIDU-US)，不僅是對百度業務發展的認可，也是看好百度未來股價上漲空間。百度近日被外媒披露，將自產電動車，就是讓這位女巴菲特相中的主因。<br />\n<br />\n在 ARK 基金敲進之前，百度股價已連日攀升，週二 (16 日) 收漲 13.83%，報 185.5 美元，刷新 2019 年 4 月以來新高，市值重回 600 億美元，達到 632 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據 ARK 基金公布的持倉資料，10 日買入逾 17 萬股百度，此為 ARK 首次買入百度股票；11 日再度加碼 32.8 萬股，連二日加碼還不夠，15 日再度敲進 47.2 萬股。<br />\n<br />\nARK 基金選取的投資標的，向來都是極具潛力的創新公司，從其過往投資組合的權重股就可窺見一斑。今年以來，ARK 持倉了包括特斯拉、串流媒體新貴 Roku、基因測序公司 Invitae、行動支付公司 Square 等，都是今年的大牛股。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連升6 日"},{"pid":"ca8e0435153e9f46d4a62a623fcce71e703e6edb","tid":2328682,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特價時段<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0170c740f71ac3b88f9e47009335687ba215f70","tid":2328682,"uid":300630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"有買ark就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfc92c0c0463446f6226c5d78bf33902d5af1e9","tid":2328682,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"其實d支那股成日唔知升咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4cde1a61615214a5203271202b72eb4d1158b99","tid":2328682,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cfc92c0c0463446f6226c5d78bf33902d5af1e9","tid":2328682,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"其實d支那股成日唔知升咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"見ark 有買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似話電動車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入咗幾百股玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bf5d9f61ef6a832b420187c3afa95850cf63cc","tid":2328682,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e15209dbf4be964479ffe0335880825c5d6a95","tid":2328682,"uid":21993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"恥笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"